OL,3,CNI Screen exceeds economy target as
OL,4,Cnew strategy launched
OL,6,FNorthern Ireland's film and television
OL,7,Findustry has contributed more than
OL,8,F#477 million to the local economy over
OL,9,Fthe last four years.
OL,11,FOn Monday, Northern Ireland Screen
OL,12,Fbrought production companies and
OL,13,Ftalent from across the world to
OL,14,FBelfast to discuss its latest strategy.
OL,16,F'The Full Picture' strategy strategy
OL,17,Fsets out its vision for the next phase
OL,18,Fof growth across the screen industries.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/6
