OL,3,CNI Screen exceeds economy target as
OL,4,Cnew strategy launched
OL,6,FOver the last four years, Northern
OL,7,FIreland Screen supported a wave of
OL,8,Fhigh-profile productions including
OL,9,FDerry Girls, How to Train Your Dragon,
OL,10,FLift, How to Get to Heaven from
OL,11,FBelfast, Blue Lights, and A Knight of
OL,12,Fthe Seven Kingdoms.
OL,14,FChief Executive of Northern Ireland
OL,15,FScreen, Richard Williams said the
OL,16,Fresults from the last strategy show
OL,17,Fwhat the sector can achieve.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/6
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
