OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F445A1776780668
OL,3,CNI Screen exceeds economy target as
OL,4,Cnew strategy launched
OL,6,F"Despite extremely challenging market
OL,7,Fconditions, we exceeded our target
OL,8,Fdelivering more than #477 million for
OL,9,Fthe local economy.
OL,11,F"The sector has also delivered a
OL,12,Fstream of hits across the last four
OL,13,Fyears growing the international
OL,14,Frelevance of the sector while our
OL,15,Fskills activities mean we're
OL,16,Fconstantly replenishing the
OL,17,Fworkforce," he said.
OL,19,F"There is intended meaning in calling
OL,20,Fthe new strategy 'The Full Picture'.
OL,26,@nD@AOUyD@KO]{D@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/6
