PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F445A1776780668
OL,3,CNI Screen exceeds economy target as
OL,4,Cnew strategy launched
OL,6,F"We want to celebrate the range of
OL,7,FNorthern Ireland Screen's activities -
OL,8,Four work in schools, archive, short
OL,9,Ffilm, Irish Language & Ulster-Scots is
OL,10,Fas important to the overall ecosystem
OL,11,Fas the high-profile projects while we
OL,12,Fsupport the widest range of screen
OL,13,Fcontent of any screen agency," Mr
OL,14,FWilliams added.
OL,16,F"The Full Picture also reflects that
OL,17,Fwe know that Northern Ireland Screen
OL,18,Fis only one cog in the wheel and that
OL,19,Four future success is dependent on
OL,20,Fenergising partnerships."
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/6
