OL,3,CNI Screen exceeds economy target as
OL,4,Cnew strategy launched
OL,6,FMr Williams said that Northern Ireland
OL,7,FScreen's main objective was "to see
OL,8,Fmore projects developed here, more
OL,9,Flocal companies growing in confidence
OL,10,Fand scale, with more people able to
OL,11,Fsee a future for themselves in this
OL,12,Findustry."
OL,14,FHe said: "This strategy sets out how
OL,15,Fwe will help make that happen."
OL,17,FCatch up with the latest UTV Live on
